---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import ImageText from '../components/ImageText.astro';
import BookingCTA from '../components/BookingCTA.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Work For Us"
	description="Interested in joining Balance Performance Physiotherapy? Send us your CV, we're always on the lookout for exceptional new additions to our team."
>
	<PageHero
		title="For Us"
		highlight="Work"
		subtitle="Interested in working for Balance? We're always on the lookout for exceptional new additions to our fantastic team."
		breadcrumb="Work For Us"
		ctaText="Get in touch"
		ctaHref="/contact-us"
	/>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Current roles"
		heading="No open roles"
		highlight="right now"
		image="/work-for-us/welcome-sign.jpg"
		imageAlt="Chalkboard welcome sign inside Balance Performance Physiotherapy"
	>
		<p>We don't have any open roles with us at the moment, but please feel free to send through your CV if anything comes up in the near future!</p>
		<p>We're always on the lookout for exceptional new additions to our fantastic team, from consultant physiotherapists and osteopaths to soft tissue therapists, strength &amp; conditioning coaches, and admin.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Apply"
		heading="Join the Balance"
		highlight="Performance team"
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/work-for-us/shop-interior.jpg"
		imageAlt="Inside the Balance Physio reception and shop"
	>
		<p>Send us your CV and a short note about what you're looking for. Include:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Your full name</li>
			<li>Phone number</li>
			<li>Email address</li>
			<li>CV (PDF preferred)</li>
		</ul>
		<p>Email everything to <a href="mailto:admin@balancephysio.com" class="inline-link">admin@balancephysio.com</a> or call <strong>020 7627 2308</strong> to chat to us directly.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<BookingCTA />
</Layout>
